\begin_inset Formula $\Diff{}{f}$
\end_inset

, in which 
\begin_inset Formula $\Diff{}{f}$
\end_inset

 is a linear differential of the form: 
\begin_inset Formula \begin{align}
	\Diff{}{f} = \sum\limits_{i=1}^m M_i(x_1,x_2,...x_m)\Diff{}{x_i}.
\end{align}
\end_inset


